2010-09-26 ho22bus-0.8.4.1
	* Fork reciteword-0.8.4 by YunQiang Su <wzssyqa@gmail.com>.
	* Changes:
	  - replace esound with aplay (done by Aron Xu).
	  - replace skin to rw(zh_CN) and rw_en(en,default). (legal consideration)
	  - replace old rwdict icon with icon of stardict.
	  - add a translatable string to determine which skin to use.
	  - not using skin in configfile temporarily.
	  - some modify of skin, make it can accept absolute path (for future system wide configfile).

